From all genes TWAS results, we conducted a gene-set enrichment analysis using the program TWAS-GSEA67 for GO terms (downloaded from MSigDB, February 2019 Gene Ontology release)68,69. TWAS-GSEA preforms first a fixed-effects linear regression on the model \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
